column8: You wretches are coming with me.
Life and death, one and the same.
Quite a mess you've made here, Zagreus.
Not if I can help it.
I have to take you back.
I have to take you now.
I'll see what I can do.
Don't know what you're expecting, giving this to me. I won't let you hold some favor over me, so here, you take this and we'll say we're settled up.
If there's a catch here I don't want to know. And, I got you something, too. Don't even think about telling anyone, either; especially Hypnos.
No, let him stay, if that's what he wants. What does it matter? He's technically allowed within these halls, but he must know he isn't welcome anymore.
Don't let it happen again. It'll be both our skins if you get caught in one of your tricks. Now get pushing, go.
You might want to stand back, there, Zag.
Think you can beat me, Zag?
Can you deal death faster than I?
What say we get things started.
I'll send you to the lowest depths.
All of you, prepare to die again.
You going to help or what?
I'm not your foe here, Zag.
Not going to fight you, Zag.
That was the last of them.
This won't go on the record.
Save some for me next time.
You took more down than I did.
Got more of them than I did, huh.
You held your own out there.
You held your own I guess.
You're not too bad at this.
You're fast, I'll give you that.
Let's call this one a draw.
You got as many as I did.
You summoned me, and I am here. Let's get this done.
I got your message and arrived as soon as possible.
You called for reinforcements. Here they are.
Went all the way again, huh.
Hang on to this for me.
Don't know what I'm supposed to do with this.
Don't know how come you're giving this to me.
If that's what you really want...
It's not my place to take something like this.
I need to ask something of you.
Need you to do something for me.
Don't stay too long in there.
Looking the other way, don't worry, Zag.
